Install VSCode


### Xampp
Download xampp linux in their site Xampp for linux
cd Downloads //enter directory
chmod 755 xampp-linux-x64-7.2.10-0-installer.run //enter package name
ls -l xampp-linux-x64-7.2.10-0-installer.run //enter package name
sudo ./xampp-linux-7.2.10-0-installer.run //enter package name


### Node

sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install nodejs
sudo apt-get install npm

sudo apt-get install nodejs npm //both

Latest Version
https://github.com/nodesource/distributions/blob/master/README.md
curl -fsSL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_14.x | sudo -E bash -
sudo apt-get install -y nodejs

### Angular
npm install -g @angular/cli
-- Permission issue
sudo npm install -g -f @angular/cli

-- Create app issue: The Schematic workflow failed
ng new myproject --skip-install

if error as run as admin then -> sudo -i

Upgrade to next version
update-manager -c

### Chrome
Download chrome and save file. Double click the saved file and install

### VLC
v20 sudo snap install vlc
